msgid "Yo kho, ānanda, evaṃ vadeyya: ‘etaparamaṃ sattā sukhaṃ somanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedentī’ti, idamassa nānujānāmi. "
msgstr "There are those who would say that this is the highest pleasure and happiness that sentient beings experience. But I don’t grant them that. "

msgctxt "mn59:8.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "mn59:8.3"
msgid "Atthānanda, etamhā sukhā aññaṃ sukhaṃ abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca. "
msgstr "Because there is another pleasure that is finer than that. "

msgctxt "mn59:8.4"
msgid "Katamañcānanda, etamhā sukhā aññaṃ sukhaṃ abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca? "
msgstr "And what is that pleasure? "

msgctxt "mn59:8.5"
msgid "Idhānanda, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā … pe … dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when, as the placing of the mind and keeping it connected are stilled, a mendicant enters and remains in the second absorption, which has the rapture and bliss born of immersion, with internal clarity and confidence, and unified mind, without placing the mind and keeping it connected. … "

msgctxt "mn59:8.6"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, ānanda, etamhā sukhā aññaṃ sukhaṃ abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya9, sc8
msgctxt "mn59:9.1"
msgid "Yo kho, ānanda, evaṃ vadeyya … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn59:9.2"
msgid "pe …. "
msgstr "There is another pleasure that is finer than that. "

msgctxt "mn59:9.3"
msgid "Katamañcānanda, etamhā sukhā aññaṃ sukhaṃ abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca? "
msgstr "And what is that pleasure? "

msgctxt "mn59:9.4"
msgid "Idhānanda, bhikkhu pītiyā ca virāgā … pe … tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "It’s when, with the fading away of rapture, a mendicant enters and remains in the third absorption, where they meditate with equanimity, mindful and aware, personally experiencing the bliss of which the noble ones declare, ‘Equanimous and mindful, one meditates in bliss.’ … "

msgctxt "mn59:9.5"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, ānanda, etamhā sukhā aññaṃ sukhaṃ abhikkantatarañca paṇītatarañca. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
